    <item>
      <title>英国预算危机前，里夫斯誓言“不会重拾紧缩政策”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 周一承诺，英国新工党政府不会恢复保守党前任政府的紧缩政策。在连续数周警告公共财政状况严峻之后，她将转向更为积极的论述。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯向纽约市捐赠者承诺发展人工智能和加密货币产业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-vows-to-grow-ai-crypto-industries-in-pitch-to-nyc-donors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯承诺，如果当选，将帮助增加对人工智能和加密货币的投资，并于周日向纽约的捐助者推介她的经济议程，称其将加强创新，并注重制定保护消费者和投资者的法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-vows-to-grow-ai-crypto-industries-in-pitch-to-nyc-donors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:28:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙总理与反对党领袖安排预算会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/portugal-s-prime-minister-opposition-leader-schedule-talks-on-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·蒙特内格罗和反对党社会党领导人佩德罗·努诺·桑托斯将于 9 月 27 日举行会谈，讨论 2025 年预算，此前双方本月早些时候未能就讨论时间安排达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/portugal-s-prime-minister-opposition-leader-schedule-talks-on-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:15:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理考虑对大公司征税以控制“严重”债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了弥补法国庞大的预算赤字并安抚国际投资者，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 决定对富人和大公司征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院临时拨款法案旨在为特勤局提供资金支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/house-stopgap-funding-proposal-seeks-boost-for-us-secret-service</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国会领导人周日公布了一项临时拨款法案，暂时维持美国政府运转至 12 月 20 日，谈判人员希望避免 10 月 1 日政府关门，并为圣诞节前不久的资金摊牌做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/house-stopgap-funding-proposal-seeks-boost-for-us-secret-service</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦超级富豪逃离税收上涨威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-22/london-wealth-drain-takes-shape-as-starmer-tax-fears-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党即将对富人实施三重打击，加速了部分英国富裕居民的移民计划]]></description>
