    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在德国州选举中再次败给极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党击败了极右翼的德国选择党，看上去将在东部勃兰登堡州继续执政，从而使总理和他的政党避免再次遭遇令人尴尬的选举挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 20:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯本周将补充其经济提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，随着 2024 年总统竞选进入最后六周，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯本周将在她的经济政策议程中添加新的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 19:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理关注企业税，警告债务问题“严重”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶表示，新政府可能会增加大企业和富人的税收，以修复失控的预算赤字并保持债券市场的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）周六，在阿拉巴马州伯明翰一处受欢迎的夜生活场所，多名枪手开枪射击，造成 4 人死亡，17 人受伤，警方称这是针对其中一名被杀害者进行的有针对性的“射击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
